<p><a name="Background" id="Background"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Dred_Scott_v._Sandford&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Background">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Background</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;"><a href="/wiki/File:DredScott.jpg" class="image" title="Portrait of Dred Scott"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/97/DredScott.jpg/200px-DredScott.jpg" width="200" height="228" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
