<li><a href="/wiki/File:Wikisource-logo.svg" class="image" title="Wikisource-logo.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Wikisource-logo.svg/16px-Wikisource-logo.svg.png" width="16" height="17" border="0" /></a> Works related to <a href="http://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Dred_Scott_v._Sandford" class="extiw" title="wikisource:Dred Scott v. Sandford">Dred Scott v. Sandford</a> at <a href="/wiki/Wikisource" title="Wikisource">Wikisource</a></li>
